testcase.name: POWERSHELL_STEP_UTILITYFUNCTIONS - Powershell Step Tests For Utility Function S-PS-UTIL-0060. User adds a variable using add_run_variables utility function in the powerShell step for one key-value pair and the value should be of type string with spaces included. Then verifies that the format of the string should be the same in the onExecute section.
